{"tid":1931572,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中共 : 中國冠狀病毒不能靠集體免疫解決 國際目前應通力合作生產有效疫苗","createTime":"2020-03-18T08:37:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T09:05:30.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f14a1466efe3acfdf677832a7480febcf1c0c1a6","tid":1931572,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T08:37:35.000Z","msg":"鍾南山：新型冠狀病毒不能靠集體免疫解決<br />\n<br />\n國家衛健委高級別專家組長鍾南山指，新型冠狀病毒傳播系數非常高，不能靠集體免疫解決問題。鍾南山指，現在無證據顯示冠狀病毒一次感染終生免疫，指從源頭預防是最古老但有效的方法，目前需要在國際合作下，生產出有效的疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n鍾南山又指，上游防控包括及時發現、檢測和隔離，都十分重要，指中國對確診病例的密切接觸者都會進行監控，認為目前新型冠狀病毒的「震中」歐洲，特別是意大利，可以做好這方面的工作，採取更積極的辦法，不要等到出現症狀才干預。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1274707&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1274707%26csid%3D261_341&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqF3jCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=849e45ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1274707&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"0dfac05f55b2edc45f9168ad3fdb1f69b07abf51","tid":1931572,"uid":55913,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T08:38:34.000Z","msg":"你快D研發俾我偷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ac499df8ff848928bca8ec5db859d2f34b3494","tid":1931572,"uid":181088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T08:39:04.000Z","msg":"你都狗撚線既"},{"pid":"1b52d8fd72d6c4e53386824fc1e83a2336b3aa8b","tid":1931572,"uid":41389,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T08:39:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">偷完藥又想偷咩呀 賊仔 咩唔係零感染啦咩？</span></span>"},{"pid":"c2b97e42be9882501ee34550ac55d1d9e2785135","tid":1931572,"uid":66547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T08:56:29.000Z","msg":"即係話中共無能力研發疫苗，叫外國研究俾佢拎黎用"},{"pid":"c4f58ee60f8c99e46bdd42e20ac629b5d9886398","tid":1931572,"uid":343754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T08:56:33.000Z","msg":"集體免疫既始祖係支那<br />\n支那係呢件事係第一個封城既國家"},{"pid":"8332233870134ed197f0907820d756e69f89074d","tid":1931572,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T08:57:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eab4057eed94b84ead18410a0b9b161bbc58c379","tid":1931572,"uid":185126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T08:59:41.000Z","msg":"唔使研發<br />\n中國已經搞掂咗壇野 防疫工作相當成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a26bcb1868548fb2d7efa1b85a9302fa7436d5c4","tid":1931572,"uid":110079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T09:00:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WZi47o8hjQg&amp;feature=push-u-sub&amp;attr_tag=HDRgmopAQx1FMbnE%3A6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWZi47o8hjQg%26feature%3Dpush-u-sub%26attr_tag%3DHDRgmopAQx1FMbnE%253A6&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqF3jCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=fdb2d4f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WZi47o8hjQg&amp;feature=push-u-sub&amp;attr_tag=HDRgmopAQx1FMbnE%3A6</a>"},{"pid":"6e3d702bce703b2ebdb9b910cbee548446952169","tid":1931572,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T09:05:30.000Z","msg":"終南山<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}